É§   â€œsimultaneousâ€ Êƒ and x (Swedish â€œsjâ€ sound)
É«   velarized (dark) l
É®   voiced alveolar lateral fricative

# Holy hell, lol
# https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Phonetic_Alphabet_chart_for_English_dialects
